<title>lmạ dʿạny rby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (lmạ dʿạny rby .. qạl ly tʿạl ạ̉rtạḥ
 ạ̉nạ ʿndy slạmk .. ʿndy lk ạ̉frạḥ)2
 (mạl ạlhm yswdk .. lyh byḥny ʿwdk)2
 kẖlyny ạ̉msk ạ̉ydk .. (wạ̉msẖyk fy njạḥ)2
 2-(lmạ smʿt ṣwth .. qlt lh yạ rby
 kyf btnạdy ʿlyã .. wạ̉nạ msẖ ṭạyq dẖnby)2
 (qạl ly dmy yṭhr .. mn kl ạlsẖrwr)2
 ạ̉nạ bạḥb ạlkẖạṭy .. (wạ̉kẖrjh llnwr)2
 3-(qlby sạʿthạ ạ̹thll .. wạmtlạ bạlrwḥ
 lmạ smʿt klạmh .. wsẖft ạljrwḥ)2
 (yạ rby bạḥbk .. whạʿysẖ lk ṭwl ʿmry)2
 hạfḍl ạ̉gẖny wạ̉htf .. (wạ̉slm lk ạ̉mry)2</lyrics>
